liquibase.ext.slf4jlogging

Class LiquibaseSlf4jLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • liquibase.ext.slf4jlogging.LiquibaseSlf4jLogger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    liquibase.logging.Logger, liquibase.servicelocator.PrioritizedService

    public class LiquibaseSlf4jLogger
extends Object
implements liquibase.logging.Logger
    Route Liquibase logging through Slf4j.

    Liquibase will automatically discover and use this logger as long as it is in liquibase.ext.* package.
